Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.79,0:06:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸡蛋+培根+哔！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸡蛋+培根+香肠+哔！
