Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:07:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哔~哔~哔~哔~哔~哔~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:03.26,Zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}好吃的哔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.59,0:07:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}好吃的哔~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}好吃的哔~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}好吃的哔~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.08,0:07:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}好吃的哔~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些全都是午餐肉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是哦 里面有各种各样的食物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连巧克力和口香糖都有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？连点心都有吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇~好想吃好想吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个..由于一般能买到的都是收藏用的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来都是自己判断要不要摄食的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:26.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摄食是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像就是吃的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正常地说就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻子醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.31,0:07:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己判断..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:35.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,责任自负..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自作自受..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.07,0:07:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 这里的全都是从特殊渠道入手的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以全都能安全食用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.47,0:07:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.97,0:07:45.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的能吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了太棒了太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐 这个要多少钱啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.21,0:07:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个一个五千元
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:55.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个一万五千元
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.73,0:07:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一个就这么贵！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.07,0:07:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很贵的啦不要乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:08:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些一个只要300元 所以不用介意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么价钱会差这么多呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不可思议呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可思议~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上味道比较好的给养都是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,市面上买不到的或者是被扣押的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以价格无论如何都会比较高
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么这个为什么便宜呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为很难吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的这么难吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛..MRE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:20.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这种给养被称为MRE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs48}不过有些人说这其实是"Meal Rejected by the Enemy"的略写
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:24.69,Zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}注：其实MRE是"Meal Ready to Eat"，即"即食"的略写
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:29.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Reject有遗弃 拒绝的意思 所以..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连敌人都拒绝的食物..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.17,0:08:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么难吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说各国军人办了给养交换会而美军的一点都没换出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.13,0:08:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会这么不好吃真让人有点感兴趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过啊 即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这里这些都是口味较好的厂家出产的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？每个厂家口味不一样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 有名厂家有三个..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了 我们去准备烧烤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把蔬菜拿过来了~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开头小火中间大火哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么咒语？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.01,0:09:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指火的大小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:16.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 用70度来煮饭能增加米的甜味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始用小火慢慢提升温度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.61,0:09:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等煮开之后就调整火力不要让米冒出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好麻烦啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.67,0:09:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用电锅不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用战车的电池吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话就没有情调了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.53,0:09:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,品尝饭盒煮出来的米饭才是露营的醍醐味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉今天的优花里活力四射呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.74,0:09:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子饿了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先烤起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 学姐她们还没..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.46,0:09:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体不会说谎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.66,0:09:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先烤起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米饭好像很快就能煮好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.08,0:09:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:09:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要稍微再等一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经开始烤了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:09:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:09:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始烤啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.55,0:10:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你们没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.38,0:10:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要烤！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多烤一些吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也要！这也要！这也要！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.68,0:10:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烧起来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.39,0:10:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烧个没停啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.23,0:10:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烧得超旺的呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.93,0:10:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:18.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水！水！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.56,0:10:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！你们在干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都湿答答了..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.59,0:10:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊..这下全完了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托您了 会长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来看看~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.13,0:10:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会..会长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借我一用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是..是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,河岛 能用的食材
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小山 那个拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.81,0:10:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饭煮好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.31,0:10:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？会长？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.77,0:11:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味道好香哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.11,0:11:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.33,0:11:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们开动啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为料理是会长的兴趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算啦算啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:19.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸~外表还真看不出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.43,0:11:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.98,0:11:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢款待！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 开始收拾吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个拿去那边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要洗的东西放这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到战车道能这么开心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为大家都很喜欢这所学校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 星星好像要掉下来一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.38,0:11:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能一直这样 早晨永远别来就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.47,0:11:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天的天气看来也会很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.27,0:11:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在比赛之前看来能再练一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.91,0:12:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就是为了这个目的才借了这个演习场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.26,0:12:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这里的话可以随心所欲地开动战车呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.86,0:12:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶诶诶？？？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:15.69,Zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}东富士演习场：横跨于富士山东岳的御殿场市，小山町，\N裾野市的陆上自卫队演习场。面积为88.09平方公里，是本州最大的练习场。
